{"thi-ap18:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap18:0.2":"Ekuposathikavagga ","thi-ap18:0.3":"Khematheriapadana ","thi-ap18:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","thi-ap18:1.2":"sabbadhammesu cakkhuma; ","thi-ap18:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","thi-ap18:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","thi-ap18:2.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","thi-ap18:2.2":"jata setthikule ahum; ","thi-ap18:2.3":"Nanaratanapajjote, ","thi-ap18:2.4":"mahasukhasamappita. ","thi-ap18:3.1":"Upetva tam mahaviram, ","thi-ap18:3.2":"assosim dhammadesanam; ","thi-ap18:3.3":"Tato jatappasadaham, ","thi-ap18:3.4":"upemi saranam jinam. ","thi-ap18:4.1":"Mataram pitarancaham, ","thi-ap18:4.2":"ayacitva vinayakam; ","thi-ap18:4.3":"Nimantayitva sattaham, ","thi-ap18:4.4":"bhojayim sahasavakam. ","thi-ap18:5.1":"Atikkante ca sattahe, ","thi-ap18:5.2":"mahapannanamuttamam; ","thi-ap18:5.3":"Bhikkhunim etadaggamhi, ","thi-ap18:5.4":"thapesi narasarathi. ","thi-ap18:6.1":"Tam sutva mudita hutva, ","thi-ap18:6.2":"puno tassa mahesino; ","thi-ap18:6.3":"Karam katvana tam thanam, ","thi-ap18:6.4":"panipacca panidahim. ","thi-ap18:7.1":"Tato mama jino aha, ","thi-ap18:7.2":"‘sijjhatam panidhi tava; ","thi-ap18:7.3":"Sasanghe me katam karam, ","thi-ap18:7.4":"appameyyaphalam taya. ","thi-ap18:8.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap18:8.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","thi-ap18:8.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","thi-ap18:8.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","thi-ap18:9.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayada, ","thi-ap18:9.2":"orasa dhammanimmita; ","thi-ap18:9.3":"Etadaggamanuppatta, ","thi-ap18:9.4":"khema nama bhavissati’. ","thi-ap18:10.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap18:10.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap18:10.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap18:10.4":"tavatimsupaga aham. ","thi-ap18:11.1":"Tato cuta yamamagam, ","thi-ap18:11.2":"tatoham tusitam gata; ","thi-ap18:11.3":"Tato ca nimmanaratim, ","thi-ap18:11.4":"vasavattipuram tato. ","thi-ap18:12.1":"Yattha yatthupapajjami, ","thi-ap18:12.2":"tassa kammassa vahasa; ","thi-ap18:12.3":"Tattha tattheva rajunam, ","thi-ap18:12.4":"mahesittamakarayim. ","thi-ap18:13.1":"Tato cuta manussatte, ","thi-ap18:13.2":"rajunam cakkavattinam; ","thi-ap18:13.3":"Mandalinanca rajunam, ","thi-ap18:13.4":"mahesittamakarayim. ","thi-ap18:14.1":"Sampattim anubhotvana, ","thi-ap18:14.2":"devesu manujesu ca; ","thi-ap18:14.3":"Sabbattha sukhita hutva, ","thi-ap18:14.4":"nekakappesu samsarim. ","thi-ap18:15.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","thi-ap18:15.2":"vipassi lokanayako; ","thi-ap18:15.3":"Uppajji carudassano, ","thi-ap18:15.4":"sabbadhammavipassako. ","thi-ap18:16.1":"Tamaham lokanayakam, ","thi-ap18:16.2":"upetva narasarathim; ","thi-ap18:16.3":"Dhammam bhanitam sutvana, ","thi-ap18:16.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","thi-ap18:17.1":"Dasavassasahassani, ","thi-ap18:17.2":"tassa virassa sasane; ","thi-ap18:17.3":"Brahmacariyam caritvana, ","thi-ap18:17.4":"yuttayoga bahussuta. ","thi-ap18:18.1":"Paccayakarakusala, ","thi-ap18:18.2":"catusaccavisarada; ","thi-ap18:18.3":"Nipuna cittakathika, ","thi-ap18:18.4":"satthusasanakarika. ","thi-ap18:19.1":"Tato cutaham tusitam, ","thi-ap18:19.2":"upapanna yasassini; ","thi-ap18:19.3":"Abhibhomi tahim anne, ","thi-ap18:19.4":"brahmacariphalenaham. ","thi-ap18:20.1":"Yattha yatthupapannaham, ","thi-ap18:20.2":"mahabhoga mahaddhana; ","thi-ap18:20.3":"Medhavini rupavati, ","thi-ap18:20.4":"vinitaparisapi ca. ","thi-ap18:21.1":"Bhavami tena kammena, ","thi-ap18:21.2":"yogena jinasasane; ","thi-ap18:21.3":"Sabba sampattiyo mayham, ","thi-ap18:21.4":"sulabha manaso piya. ","thi-ap18:22.1":"Yopi me bhavate bhatta, ","thi-ap18:22.2":"yattha yattha gatayapi; ","thi-ap18:22.3":"Vimaneti na mam koci, ","thi-ap18:22.4":"patipattibalena me. ","thi-ap18:23.1":"Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","thi-ap18:23.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","thi-ap18:23.3":"Namena konagamano, ","thi-ap18:23.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","thi-ap18:24.1":"Tada hi baranasiyam, ","thi-ap18:24.2":"susamiddhakulappaja; ","thi-ap18:24.3":"Dhananjani sumedha ca, ","thi-ap18:24.4":"ahampi ca tayo jana. ","thi-ap18:25.1":"Sangharamamadasimha, ","thi-ap18:25.2":"danasahayika pure; ","thi-ap18:25.3":"Sanghassa ca viharampi, ","thi-ap18:25.4":"uddissa karika mayam. ","thi-ap18:26.1":"Tato cuta mayam sabba, ","thi-ap18:26.2":"tavatimsupaga ahum; ","thi-ap18:26.3":"Yasasa aggatam patta, ","thi-ap18:26.4":"manussesu tatheva ca. ","thi-ap18:27.1":"Imasmimyeva kappamhi, ","thi-ap18:27.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","thi-ap18:27.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","thi-ap18:27.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","thi-ap18:28.1":"Upatthako mahesissa, ","thi-ap18:28.2":"tada asi narissaro; ","thi-ap18:28.3":"Kasiraja kiki nama, ","thi-ap18:28.4":"baranasipuruttame. ","thi-ap18:29.1":"Tassasim jetthika dhita, ","thi-ap18:29.2":"samani iti vissuta; ","thi-ap18:29.3":"Dhammam sutva jinaggassa, ","thi-ap18:29.4":"pabbajjam samarocayim. ","thi-ap18:30.1":"Anujani na no tato, ","thi-ap18:30.2":"agareva tada mayam; ","thi-ap18:30.3":"Visavassasahassani, ","thi-ap18:30.4":"vicarimha atandita. ","thi-ap18:31.1":"Komaribrahmacariyam, ","thi-ap18:31.2":"rajakanna sukhedhita; ","thi-ap18:31.3":"Buddhopatthananirata, ","thi-ap18:31.4":"mudita satta dhitaro. ","thi-ap18:32.1":"Samani samanagutta ca, ","thi-ap18:32.2":"bhikkhuni bhikkhudayika; ","thi-ap18:32.3":"Dhamma ceva sudhamma ca, ","thi-ap18:32.4":"sattami sanghadayika. ","thi-ap18:33.1":"Aham uppalavanna ca, ","thi-ap18:33.2":"patacara ca kundala; ","thi-ap18:33.3":"Kisagotami dhammadinna, ","thi-ap18:33.4":"visakha hoti sattami. ","thi-ap18:34.1":"Kadaci so naradicco, ","thi-ap18:34.2":"dhammam desesi abbhutam; ","thi-ap18:34.3":"Mahanidanasuttantam, ","thi-ap18:34.4":"sutva tam pariyapunim. ","thi-ap18:35.1":"Tehi kammehi sukatehi, ","thi-ap18:35.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap18:35.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap18:35.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap18:36.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","thi-ap18:36.2":"sakalaya puruttame; ","thi-ap18:36.3":"Ranno maddassa dhitamhi, ","thi-ap18:36.4":"manapa dayita piya. ","thi-ap18:37.1":"Saha me jatamattamhi, ","thi-ap18:37.2":"khemam tamhi pure ahu; ","thi-ap18:37.3":"Tato khemati namam me, ","thi-ap18:37.4":"gunato upapajjatha. ","thi-ap18:38.1":"Yadaham yobbanam patta, ","thi-ap18:38.2":"rupalavannabhusita; ","thi-ap18:38.3":"Tada adasi mam tato, ","thi-ap18:38.4":"bimbisarassa rajino. ","thi-ap18:39.1":"Tassaham suppiya asim, ","thi-ap18:39.2":"rupake layane rata; ","thi-ap18:39.3":"Rupanam dosavaditi, ","thi-ap18:39.4":"na upesim mahadayam. ","thi-ap18:40.1":"Bimbisaro tada raja, ","thi-ap18:40.2":"mamanuggahabuddhiya; ","thi-ap18:40.3":"Vannayitva veluvanam, ","thi-ap18:40.4":"gayake gapayi mamam. ","thi-ap18:41.1":"Rammam veluvanam yena, ","thi-ap18:41.2":"na dittham sugatalayam; ","thi-ap18:41.3":"Na tena nandanam dittham, ","thi-ap18:41.4":"iti mannamase mayam. ","thi-ap18:42.1":"Yena veluvanam dittham, ","thi-ap18:42.2":"naranandananandanam; ","thi-ap18:42.3":"Sudittham nandanam tena, ","thi-ap18:42.4":"amarindasunandanam. ","thi-ap18:43.1":"Vihaya nandanam deva, ","thi-ap18:43.2":"otaritva mahitalam; ","thi-ap18:43.3":"Rammam veluvanam disva, ","thi-ap18:43.4":"na tappanti suvimhita. ","thi-ap18:44.1":"Rajapunnena nibbattam, ","thi-ap18:44.2":"buddhapunnena bhusitam; ","thi-ap18:44.3":"Ko vatta tassa nissesam, ","thi-ap18:44.4":"vanassa gunasancayam. ","thi-ap18:45.1":"Tam sutva vanasamiddham, ","thi-ap18:45.2":"mama sotamanoharam; ","thi-ap18:45.3":"Datthukama tamuyyanam, ","thi-ap18:45.4":"ranno arocayim tada. ","thi-ap18:46.1":"Mahata parivarena, ","thi-ap18:46.2":"tada ca so mahipati; ","thi-ap18:46.3":"Mam pesesi tamuyyanam, ","thi-ap18:46.4":"dassanaya samussukam. ","thi-ap18:47.1":"‘Gaccha passa mahabhoge, ","thi-ap18:47.2":"vanam nettarasayanam; ","thi-ap18:47.3":"Yam sada bhati siriya, ","thi-ap18:47.4":"sugatabhanuranjitam’. ","thi-ap18:48.1":"‘Yada ca pindaya muni, ","thi-ap18:48.2":"giribbajapuruttamam; ","thi-ap18:48.3":"Pavitthoham tadayeva, ","thi-ap18:48.4":"vanam datthumupagamim’. ","thi-ap18:49.1":"Tada tam phullavipinam, ","thi-ap18:49.2":"nanabhamarakujitam; ","thi-ap18:49.3":"Kokilagitasahitam, ","thi-ap18:49.4":"mayuragananaccitam. ","thi-ap18:50.1":"Appasaddamanakinnam, ","thi-ap18:50.2":"nanacankamabhusitam; ","thi-ap18:50.3":"Kutimandapasankinnam, ","thi-ap18:50.4":"yogivaravirajitam. ","thi-ap18:51.1":"Vicaranti amannissam, ","thi-ap18:51.2":"‘saphalam nayanam mama’; ","thi-ap18:51.3":"Tatthapi tarunam bhikkhum, ","thi-ap18:51.4":"yuttam disva vicintayim. ","thi-ap18:52.1":"‘Idise vipine ramme, ","thi-ap18:52.2":"thitoyam navayobbane; ","thi-ap18:52.3":"Vasantamiva kantena, ","thi-ap18:52.4":"rupena ca samanvito. ","thi-ap18:53.1":"Nisinno rukkhamulamhi, ","thi-ap18:53.2":"mundo sanghatiparuto; ","thi-ap18:53.3":"Jhayate vatayam bhikkhu, ","thi-ap18:53.4":"hitva visayajam ratim. ","thi-ap18:54.1":"Nanu nama gahatthena, ","thi-ap18:54.2":"kamam bhutva yathasukham; ","thi-ap18:54.3":"Paccha jinnena dhammoyam, ","thi-ap18:54.4":"caritabbo subhaddako’. ","thi-ap18:55.1":"‘Sunnakan’ti viditvana, ","thi-ap18:55.2":"‘gandhageham jinalayam’; ","thi-ap18:55.3":"Upetva jinamaddakkham, ","thi-ap18:55.4":"udayantamva bhakaram. ","thi-ap18:56.1":"Ekakam sukhamasinam, ","thi-ap18:56.2":"bijamanam varitthiya; ","thi-ap18:56.3":"Disvanevam vicintesim, ","thi-ap18:56.4":"‘nayam lukho narasabho. ","thi-ap18:57.1":"Sa kanna kanakabhasa, ","thi-ap18:57.2":"padumananalocana; ","thi-ap18:57.3":"Bimbotthi kundadasana, ","thi-ap18:57.4":"manonettarasayana. ","thi-ap18:58.1":"Hemadolabhasavana, ","thi-ap18:58.2":"kalikakarasutthani; ","thi-ap18:58.3":"Vedimajjhava sussoni, ","thi-ap18:58.4":"rambhoru carubhusana. ","thi-ap18:59.1":"Rattamsakupasambyana, ","thi-ap18:59.2":"nilamatthanivasana; ","thi-ap18:59.3":"Atappaneyyarupena, ","thi-ap18:59.4":"hasabhavasamanvita’. ","thi-ap18:60.1":"Disva tamevam cintesim, ","thi-ap18:60.2":"‘ahoyamabhirupini; ","thi-ap18:60.3":"Na mayanena nettena, ","thi-ap18:60.4":"ditthapubba kudacanam’. ","thi-ap18:61.1":"Tato jarabhibhuta sa, ","thi-ap18:61.2":"vivanna vikatanana; ","thi-ap18:61.3":"Bhinnadanta setasira, ","thi-ap18:61.4":"salala vadanasuci. ","thi-ap18:62.1":"Sankhittakanna setakkhi, ","thi-ap18:62.2":"lambasubhapayodhara; ","thi-ap18:62.3":"Valivitatasabbangi, ","thi-ap18:62.4":"siravitatadehini. ","thi-ap18:63.1":"Natanga dandadutiya, ","thi-ap18:63.2":"upphasulikata kisa; ","thi-ap18:63.3":"Pavedhamana patita, ","thi-ap18:63.4":"nissasanti muhum muhum. ","thi-ap18:64.1":"Tato me asi samvego, ","thi-ap18:64.2":"abbhuto lomahamsano; ","thi-ap18:64.3":"‘Dhiratthu rupam asucim, ","thi-ap18:64.4":"ramante yattha balisa’. ","thi-ap18:65.1":"Tada mahakaruniko, ","thi-ap18:65.2":"disva samviggamanasam; ","thi-ap18:65.3":"Udaggacitto sugato, ","thi-ap18:65.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","thi-ap18:66.1":"‘Aturam asucim putim, ","thi-ap18:66.2":"passa kheme samussayam; ","thi-ap18:66.3":"Uggharantam paggharantam, ","thi-ap18:66.4":"balanam abhinanditam. ","thi-ap18:67.1":"Asubhaya cittam bhavehi, ","thi-ap18:67.2":"ekaggam susamahitam; ","thi-ap18:67.3":"Sati kayagata tyatthu, ","thi-ap18:67.4":"nibbida bahula bhava. ","thi-ap18:68.1":"Yatha idam tatha etam, ","thi-ap18:68.2":"yatha etam tatha idam; ","thi-ap18:68.3":"Ajjhattanca bahiddha ca, ","thi-ap18:68.4":"kaye chandam virajaya. ","thi-ap18:69.1":"Animittanca bhavehi, ","thi-ap18:69.2":"mananusayamujjaha; ","thi-ap18:69.3":"Tato manabhisamaya, ","thi-ap18:69.4":"upasanta carissasi. ","thi-ap18:70.1":"Ye ragarattanupatanti sotam, ","thi-ap18:70.2":"Sayam katam makkatakova jalam; ","thi-ap18:70.3":"Etampi chetvana paribbajanti, ","thi-ap18:70.4":"Anapekkhino kamasukham pahaya’. ","thi-ap18:71.1":"Tato kallitacittam mam, ","thi-ap18:71.2":"natvana narasarathi; ","thi-ap18:71.3":"Mahanidanam desesi, ","thi-ap18:71.4":"suttantam vinayaya me. ","thi-ap18:72.1":"Sutva suttantasettham tam, ","thi-ap18:72.2":"pubbasannamanussarim; ","thi-ap18:72.3":"Tattha thitavaham santi, ","thi-ap18:72.4":"dhammacakkhum visodhayim. ","thi-ap18:73.1":"Nipatitva mahesissa, ","thi-ap18:73.2":"padamulamhi tavade; ","thi-ap18:73.3":"Accayam desanatthaya, ","thi-ap18:73.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","thi-ap18:74.1":"‘Namo te sabbadassavi, ","thi-ap18:74.2":"namo te karunakara; ","thi-ap18:74.3":"Namo te tinnasamsara, ","thi-ap18:74.4":"namo te amatamdada. ","thi-ap18:75.1":"Ditthigahanapakkhanda, ","thi-ap18:75.2":"kamaragavimohita; ","thi-ap18:75.3":"Taya samma upayena, ","thi-ap18:75.4":"vinita vinaye rata. ","thi-ap18:76.1":"Adassanena vibhoga, ","thi-ap18:76.2":"tadisanam mahesinam; ","thi-ap18:76.3":"Anubhonti mahadukkham, ","thi-ap18:76.4":"satta samsarasagare. ","thi-ap18:77.1":"Yadaham lokasaranam, ","thi-ap18:77.2":"aranam aranantagum; ","thi-ap18:77.3":"Naddasami adurattham, ","thi-ap18:77.4":"desayami tamaccayam. ","thi-ap18:78.1":"Mahahitam varadadam, ","thi-ap18:78.2":"ahitoti visankita; ","thi-ap18:78.3":"Nopesim rupanirata, ","thi-ap18:78.4":"desayami tamaccayam’. ","thi-ap18:79.1":"Tada madhuranigghoso, ","thi-ap18:79.2":"mahakaruniko jino; ","thi-ap18:79.3":"Avoca tittha khemeti, ","thi-ap18:79.4":"sincanto amatena mam. ","thi-ap18:80.1":"Tada panamya sirasa, ","thi-ap18:80.2":"katva ca nam padakkhinam; ","thi-ap18:80.3":"Gantva disva narapatim, ","thi-ap18:80.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","thi-ap18:81.1":"‘Aho samma upayo te, ","thi-ap18:81.2":"cintitoyamarindama; ","thi-ap18:81.3":"Vanadassanakamaya, ","thi-ap18:81.4":"dittho nibbanato muni. ","thi-ap18:82.1":"Yadi te ruccate raja, ","thi-ap18:82.2":"sasane tassa tadino; ","thi-ap18:82.3":"Pabbajissami rupeham, ","thi-ap18:82.4":"nibbinna munivanina’. ","thi-ap18:83.1":"Dutiyam bhanavaram. ","thi-ap18:84.1":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","thi-ap18:84.2":"tadaha sa mahipati; ","thi-ap18:84.3":"‘Anujanami te bhadde, ","thi-ap18:84.4":"pabbajja tava sijjhatu’. ","thi-ap18:85.1":"Pabbajitva tada caham, ","thi-ap18:85.2":"addhamase upatthite; ","thi-ap18:85.3":"Dipodayanca bhedanca, ","thi-ap18:85.4":"disva samviggamanasa. ","thi-ap18:86.1":"Nibbinna sabbasankhare, ","thi-ap18:86.2":"paccayakarakovida; ","thi-ap18:86.3":"Caturoghe atikkamma, ","thi-ap18:86.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","thi-ap18:87.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi asim, ","thi-ap18:87.2":"dibbaya sotadhatuya; ","thi-ap18:87.3":"Cetopariyananassa, ","thi-ap18:87.4":"vasi capi bhavamaham. ","thi-ap18:88.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap18:88.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap18:88.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","thi-ap18:88.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thi-ap18:89.1":"Atthadhammaniruttisu, ","thi-ap18:89.2":"patibhane tatheva ca; ","thi-ap18:89.3":"Parisuddham mama nanam, ","thi-ap18:89.4":"uppannam buddhasasane. ","thi-ap18:90.1":"Kusalaham visuddhisu, ","thi-ap18:90.2":"kathavatthuvisarada; ","thi-ap18:90.3":"Abhidhammanayannu ca, ","thi-ap18:90.4":"vasippattamhi sasane. ","thi-ap18:91.1":"Tato toranavatthusmim, ","thi-ap18:91.2":"ranna kosalasamina; ","thi-ap18:91.3":"Pucchita nipune panhe, ","thi-ap18:91.4":"byakaronti yathatatham. ","thi-ap18:92.1":"Tada sa raja sugatam, ","thi-ap18:92.2":"upasankamma pucchatha; ","thi-ap18:92.3":"Tatheva buddho byakasi, ","thi-ap18:92.4":"yatha te byakata maya. ","thi-ap18:93.1":"Jino tasmim gune tuttho, ","thi-ap18:93.2":"etadagge thapesi mam; ","thi-ap18:93.3":"Mahapannanamaggati, ","thi-ap18:93.4":"bhikkhuninam naruttamo. ","thi-ap18:94.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap18:94.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap18:94.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap18:95.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap18:95.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap18:95.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap18:96.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap18:96.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap18:96.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap18:97.1":"Ittham sudam khema bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap18:98.1":"Khematheriyapadanam atthamam. "}